des:
Luminus Smart products integrate with Amazon Alexa in any Echo or Alexa Built-in product to make controlling your smart lighting or other smart products simple 

Installation guide:
1. Download our "Luminus"app on Google Play or iOS App Store;
2. Launch the app and register for an account
3. Turn on your Luminus LED Smart Bulb or other product and connect them with the app;
4. You can rename Luminus products in the app. If you rename a bulb “Bedroom Light”, then Alexa will understand that name after discovering the devices in Step 9;
5. Download the Amazon Alexa app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect with Alexa app;
6. Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Luminus Smart”;
7. Click Enable skill of "Luminus Smart", then input your account username, password, and region on the following page;
8. Talk to your Alexa app or any of your Alexa Built-in devices and say, “Discover devices”. Wait until Alexa says "Discover is completed";
9. Now you can talk to Alexa app or any of your Alexa Built-in devices control your Luminus products.

Here are the voice commands you can use with Alexa and Luminus Smart:

Lights:
* Alexa, turn on my living room light
* Alexa, turn off my living room light
* Alexa, dim my living room light
* Alexa, brighten my living room light
* Alexa, set the living room light to 20 percent
* Alexa, set bedroom light to green.
* Alexa, set bedroom light to daylight.
